Package eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.collection

Class AssetCategoryResponsesWrapper

java.lang.Object
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.ResponseWrapper
eu.datacrop.maize.model_repository.commons.wrappers.collection.AssetCategoryResponsesWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AssetCategoryResponsesWrapper extends ResponseWrapper implements Serializable
This class wraps the responses travelling from the persistence layer back to the API for a more complete reporting of problems / unsuccessful requests on Asset Categories. Used for Collections (as opposed to a Single Object).
Since:
version 0.4.0
Author:
Angela-Maria Despotopoulou [Athens, Greece]
